Exploratores OSINT Suite (Skill + MCP)
======================================

This project is a derivative work of the Exploratores OSINT Toolkit.

Original work:
  Exploratores OSINT Toolkit 3.4.1
  Author: Ramingo (SOsintOps)
  Source: https://github.com/SOsintOps/Exploratores
  Licence: GNU Affero General Public License v3.0 (AGPL-3.0)

This derivative:
  - Ports the toolkit's search catalog (search-library.js) into a language-neutral
    catalog.json, enriched with the human-readable labels from the toolkit's HTML.
  - Re-implements the indicator classifier (indicator-classifier.js), the input
    validators (validators.js) and the URL-substitution logic (main.js) in Python.
  - Re-implements the IBAN structural validation (ibankit country table + ISO 13616
    mod-97) and the Redactor concept in Python.
  - Packages the result as (1) an AI Agent Skill and (2) an MCP server.

As a derivative of an AGPL-3.0 work, this project is also distributed under the
AGPL-3.0. See the LICENSE file for the full text.

Bundled third-party components in the ORIGINAL toolkit (CyberChef, ibankit,
libphonenumber) retain their own upstream licences and are NOT redistributed here;
only the country length/name table from ibankit was ported as data.
